  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd ; \u0b87\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 15 \u0bae\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One more dies while waiting in fuel line; So far 15 deaths have been recorded",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 60-year-old man from Moratuwa area who was waiting in queue for fuel in Kalutara-Byakala area has died.",
        "According to the hospital information, the said person suddenly recovered while waiting in the queue and died after being admitted to Nagoda Hospital.",
        "Meanwhile, as the economic crisis in the country has increased, people have to wait in queues for days for fuel, gas etc.",
        "It is noteworthy that the number of people who died while waiting in the fuel line has increased to 15 in recent days.",
        "At the same time, the killings are carried out by making people wait in queues for a long time, physically and psychologically weakening them, and what is the compensation for these deaths and the families affected by it? It is noteworthy that United People's Shakti Member of Parliament Tushara Indunil raised a question with the government yesterday."
      ],
